20-08-29T19:02:01.000Z","msg":"食過竹地小館 性價比高 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22595a74b4c74a8efb1936a229eb8c301752381","tid":2169732,"uid":54223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T19:07:38.000Z","msg":"正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}